<plot>Ray Martin is an insurance salesman in Monterey CA. Nine years ago he lost his only daughter to disability and disease. He is now head instructor at the program that allowed his daughter not only to live as long as she did, but enjoy every minute of it. This short documentary tells the story of the program that continues to improve the lives of children who suffer from disability.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?513556</url></doc>
